text.section:
The articles of dissolution shall state:
The name of the cooperative and the address of its principal office;
The date on which the certificate of election to dissolve was accepted for record by the Department;
That there are no actions pending against the cooperative;
That all debts, obligations, and liabilities of the cooperative have been discharged, or that adequate provision has been made for their discharge;
That the articles are executed in accordance with this subtitle; and
That the provisions of this section have been complied with.
